quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  76,26,aur raat ko barri raat taq sjday karo aur is ki paki bayan karte raho
  76,27,yeh log duniya ko dost rakhtay hain aur ( qayamat ke ) bhaari din ko pas pusht chhorey dete hain
  76,28,hum ne un ko pedakiya aur un ke maqabil ko mazboot banaya. aur agar hum chahain to un ke badlay un hi ki terhan aur log le ayen
  76,29,yeh to nasiyaat hai. jo chahay apne perwar-digaar ki taraf pounchanay ka rasta ikhtiyar kere
  76,30,aur tum kuch bhi nahi chaah satke magar jo khuda ko Manzoor ho. be shak khuda jan-nay wala hikmat wala hai
  76,31,jis ko chahta hai apni rehmat mein daakhil karleta hai aur zaalmon ke liye is ne dukh dainay wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  77,1,hawaon ki qasam jo naram naram chalti hain
  77,2,phir zor pakar kar jhakar ho jati hain
  77,3,aur ( baadalon ko ) phaar kar phela deti hain
  77,4,phir un ko phaar kar judda judda kar deti hain
  77,5,phir firshton ki qasam jo wahi laatay hain
  77,6,taakay izr ( rafa ) kardiya jaye ya dar suna diya jaye
  77,7,ke jis baat ka tum se wadakiya jata hai woh ho kar rahay gi
  77,8,jab taron ki chamak jati rahay
  77,9,aur jab aasman phatt jaye
  77,10,aur jab pahar uday uday phrin
  77,11,aur jab paighambar faraham kiye jayen
  77,12,bhala ( un umoor mein ) takheer kis din ke liye ki gayi ?
  77,13,faislay ke din ke liye
  77,14,aur tumhekiya khabar ke faislay ka dinkiya hai ?
  77,15,is din jhutlanay walon ke liye kharabi hai
  77,16,kiya hum ne pehlay logon ko halaak nahi kar dala
  77,17,phir un pichlon ko bhi un ke peechay bhaij dete hain
  77,18,hum gunahgaaron ke sath aisa hikiya karte hain
  77,19,is din jhutlanay walon ki kharabi hai
